{
  "text": "All experimental procedures using animals were approved by the Institutional Animal Care and Use Committee at Boston University School of Medicine. Tg2576 (APP) mice expressing the Swedish mutation of human APP (isoform 695) were obtained from Drs. G. Carlson and K. Ashe and maintained in B6/129 background [CITATION_1] . TTBK1 transgenic mice (Line 141) harboring human TTBK1 genomic fragment were maintained in B6/129 background as described previously [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] . Tg2576 mice were crossed with TTBK1 mice to generate APP, TTBK1, APP/TTBK1 and non-transgenic (non-Tg) littermates, and tested at 10-11 months of age.",
